<![CDATA[<b style="font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#cc0000" size="4">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font></b><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#cc0000" size="4"><br></font></b></div><div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Youth Assessor Training at Ignite 2015&nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Congratulations on graduating from the National Citizen Service programme and welcome to our fantastic alumni programme called The Challenge Society. Over the summer you expressed your interest in volunteering as a Youth Assessor and helping us choose the very best mentors and leaders for future NCS programmes.&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Our first training event is taking place at our launch event for The Challenge Society called Ignite 2015!&nbsp;</font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#cc0000">Where:</font>&nbsp;Goldsmiths University, New Cross, SE14 6NW.</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#cc0000">When:</font>&nbsp;Saturday 28th of November between 11:00 and 17:00.</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="text-align: center; font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#cc0000"><a href="http://tcssouthlondon.co.uk/ignite-2015/">Click here to reserve your space!&nbsp;</a></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><font color="#cc0000"><b style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Featuring special guests&nbsp;</span></font></b><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Aaron Roach Bridgeman from SBTV and a&nbsp;</span>performance<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;by Afrikan Boy!&nbsp;</span></font></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">In addition to becoming a Youth Assessor</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;for The Challenge, Ignite 2015 is all about you and your future. Get involved in CV and interview workshops, personal statement sessions, money management workshops and meet a huge range of professionals!&nbsp;</span></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Really looking forward to seeing you there,&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Rhiannon&nbsp;</b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Graduate Associate Manager - South East London</b></div></div>]]></td>
